<br>
Today after 16+ hours of camping the mob the thing finally spawned. Had my nec parked there so I just used sense the dead and moved to it, pet behind me.<br>
<br>
I followed it a ways just to watch it roam and take out some of the roamers in the area.<br>
<br>
Well when I actually engaged the Ancient Jarsath, it knocked my pet down pretty quick but my nukes kept their health pretty even until the jarsath was around 20% where my pet died. Right after that a drovlarg agroed the ancient jarsath and killed it, causing the corpse to vanish.<br>
<br>
Btw I did try to land the final nuke, but it got interrupted somehow...(gotta look into log)...<br>
<br>
Something seems pretty wrong with that, since I didnt kill drovlargs to spawn the jarsath and while I was following it it passed a ton of drovlargs and non agroed it.<br>
<br>
Asking a GM about it tomorrow but any comments / support on this would be greatly appreciated. <p> <FONT COLOR="FFFFFF" SIZE="2"><DIV style="position:relative; width=80%; filter:glow(color=FF0000)"><B>Baron Sephik Striffe</B>
